Interface SubqueryExpression

All Superinterfaces:
Expression, PropertyAccessor, Visitable
All Known Implementing Classes:
CollectExpression, CountExpression, ExistentialSubquery
public sealed interface SubqueryExpression extends Expression permits ExistentialSubquery, CountExpression, CollectExpression
A sub-query expression can either be an EXISTS-tential or a COUNT expression as of Neo4j 5.
